{"data":[{"date":"10:12 06/08","title":"M\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo \u1edf Juventus \"kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp\" \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ebf n\u00e0o?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/31/muc-luong-cua-cristiano-ronaldo-o-juventus-khung-khiep-den-the-nao.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo thu\u1ed9c h\u00e0ng top th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu ch\u1ec9 so v\u1edbi m\u1eb7t b\u1eb1ng chung \u1edf Serie A, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u00f2n th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 Juventus ch\u1ecbu ch\u01a1i th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu Cr7.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Juventus ch\u1ecbu ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu Ronaldo<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi ra 100 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Cristiano Ronaldo, Juventus t\u1eebng b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3 khi b\u1ecf ng\u1ea7n \u1ea5y ti\u1ec1n cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, Juventus c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng toan t\u00ednh ri\u00eang khi Ronaldo gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin gia t\u0103ng v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 m\u1eb7t t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo toi Juventus\" title=\"Ronaldo toi Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/muc-luong-cua-cristiano-ronaldo-o-juventus-khung-khiep-den-the-nao.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>M\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo g\u1ea5p h\u01a1n ba l\u1ea7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ee9ng sau t\u1ea1i Serie A.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, Juventus s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t m\u1ed7i n\u0103m 31 tri\u1ec7u euro ti\u1ec1n l\u01b0\u01a1ng cho Ronaldo, con s\u1ed1 c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn n\u1ebfu so v\u1edbi m\u1eb7t b\u1eb1ng chung c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Serie A v\u1ed1n kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 d\u01b0 d\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh. \u0110\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u1ecbu ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Juventus, h\u00e3y so m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo v\u1edbi Gonzalo Higuain, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 hai t\u1ea1i Serie A.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Higuain v\u1eeba r\u1eddi Juventus gia nh\u1eadp AC Milan v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Ronaldo. M\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng Higuain nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i AC Milan cao th\u1ee9 hai t\u1ea1i Serie A v\u1edbi con s\u1ed1 9 tri\u1ec7u euro m\u1ed7i n\u0103m, ch\u01b0a b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n ba m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Juventus th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb v\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n l\u01b0\u01a1ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3 cho Ronaldo m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u0169ng cho th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt kh\u00e1c r\u1eb1ng Juventus c\u00f3 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Serie A. Trong top 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao nh\u1ea5t Serie A hi\u1ec7n nay, Juventus chi\u1ebfm \u0111\u1ebfn 3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 Ronaldo (31 tri\u1ec7u euro), Paulo Dybala (7) v\u00e0 Douglas Costa (6). Hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf AC Milan l\u00e0 Higuain (9) v\u00e0 Donnarumma (6).&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Juventus c\u0169ng chi ra \u0111\u1ebfn 239.9 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean g\u1ed3m Mattia Perin, Leonardo Bonucci, Joao Cancelo, Emre Can v\u00e0 Ronaldo.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Juventus h\u00e8 2018:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-juventus-real-van-rat-dang-so-du-khong-co-ronaldo-180-193768.html\">HLV Juventus: Real v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-real-madrid-31-juventus-icc-2018-329-193746.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Real Madrid 3-1 Juventus (ICC 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/leonardo-bonucci-khong-xin-loi-sau-khi-tro-lai-juventus-176-193737.html\">Leonardo Bonucci quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng xin l\u1ed7i sau khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/real-madrid-vs-juventus-tran-dau-icc-2018-372-193731.html\">Real Madrid 3-1 Juventus (KT): Los Blancos t\u01b0\u01a1i m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Lopetegui ti\u00eau di\u1ec7t g\u1ecdn B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/goc-nhin-tai-hop-cuu-den-juventus-kho-lam-nen-chuyen-o-champions-league-176-193654.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: T\u00e1i h\u1ee3p &ldquo;c\u1eebu \u0111en&rdquo;, Juventus kh\u00f3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n \u1edf Champions League</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tan-man/tom-cruise-cristiano-ronaldo-tuoi-tac-co-gi-ma-bat-kha-thi-392-192631.html\">Tom Cruise - Cristiano Ronaldo: Tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c c\u00f3 g\u00ec m\u00e0 b\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 thi</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)&nbsp;</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5142","checkdouble":"193834"},{"date":"11:24 06/08","title":"D\u01b0 \u00e2m U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1-0 U23 Oman: Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 can \u0111\u1ea3m","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/du-am-u23-viet-nam-10-u23-oman-chien-thang-cua-su-can-dam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u01b0\u1eddng thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb T\u00e2y \u00c1 th\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i khi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf m\u1ed9t tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 suy ngh\u0129 kh\u00e1c.</h2><h2>Khi n\u1ed7i s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i \u0111\u00e3 tan bi\u1ebfn<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 T\u00e2y \u00c1 n\u00f3i chung v\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Oman n\u00f3i ri\u00eang trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c l\u1edbn v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Ch\u1eb3ng n\u00f3i \u0111\u00e2u xa, t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i Asian Cup 2004 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eebng hai l\u1eadp ch\u1ea1m m\u1eb7t \u0110T Oman v\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u1edf c\u1ea3 hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111i v\u00e0 v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 0-6 v\u00e0 0-2.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a h\u01a1n 10 n\u0103m v\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc. C\u00f2n \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, khi m\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang chuy\u1ec3n m\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd nh\u1edd ngu\u1ed3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ed3i d\u00e0o, c\u00f3 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n, l\u00f2 \u0111\u1ea1o t\u1ea1o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111ang d\u1ea7n thay \u0111\u1ed5i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u01a1n h\u1ebft, d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1ebb Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng l\u00ean m\u1ed9t t\u1ea7m cao m\u1edbi. Sau ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 gia t\u0103ng nhanh ch\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1-0 U23 Oman Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 can \u0111\u1ea3m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1-0 U23 Oman Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 can \u0111\u1ea3m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/38544470_1862150223877255_4595212014233583616_n.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018 theo c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m cho h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ef1 ti khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf. D\u00f9 b\u1ecb x\u1ebfp \u1edf th\u1ec3 c\u1eeda d\u01b0\u1edbi v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 thua k\u00e9m v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f9ng s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n d\u01b0\u1edbi t\u00e0i c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00f4i c\u00f4ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1-0 U23 Oman, d\u00f9 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 x\u00e1o tr\u1ed9n, th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 t\u1edbi hai \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00e1c nhau. D\u00f9 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft \u1edf hai \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ed1ng nhau nh\u01b0ng t\u1ef1u chung m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 tr\u00ean h\u1ebft, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 bi\u1ebft run s\u1ee3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u00fac n\u00e0y, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta \u0111ang tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, li\u00ean t\u1ee5c pressing to\u00e0n s\u00e2n d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c sung m\u00e3n. S\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin c\u0169ng gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng che b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 tung ra nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n kh\u00e1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1-0 U23 Oman Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 can \u0111\u1ea3m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1-0 U23 Oman Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 can \u0111\u1ea3m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-oman-19h30-ngay-058-co-hoi-cho-kep-phu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110\u00e1 pressing to\u00e0n s\u00e2n, kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i tranh ch\u1ea5p l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i bi\u1ebfn h\u00f3a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng pha ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p trung l\u1ed9, b\u1eadt t\u01b0\u1edfng 1-2, hay ch\u1ecdc khe v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i d\u00e3n bi\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ea7n l\u00e0m cho l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u1edf n\u00ean nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u00e0 c\u0169ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u01a1n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i nh\u01b0 \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu c\u0169ng t\u1ef1 tin l\u00ean tham gia t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m ghi b\u00e0n, m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f3m l\u1ea1i, chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 nh\u1edd t\u00e0i c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park hay s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao, m\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n n\u00f3 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 can \u0111\u1ea3m, t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i c\u1ee7a l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng t\u1ea1o n\u00ean nh\u1eefng k\u1ef3 t\u00edch \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng U23 ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c 'gi\u1eef l\u1eeda' t\u1edbi&nbsp;ASIAD<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1-0 U23 Oman&nbsp;\u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo&nbsp;\u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i n\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u khi m\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018. <o:p></o:p>\u0110\u00edch \u0111\u1ebfn l\u1edbn h\u01a1n v\u1edbi h\u1ecd l\u00fac n\u00e0y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i Indonesia trong \u00edt ng\u00e0y n\u1eefa. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang g\u1eb7p th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c l\u1edbn trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng. <o:p></o:p>V\u00ec v\u1eady, nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u1eef l\u1eeda t\u1ef1 tin cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e2m l\u00fd v\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho ASIAD 2018.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc ra t\u1eeb s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n chung cu\u1ed9c, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. V\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd kh\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1 h\u01a1n trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Viet Nam\" title=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/U23-Viet-Nam-vs-U23-Palestine-Cho-man-tai-xuat-cua-nhung-nguoi-h-hinh-anh.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c 'gi\u1eef l\u1eeda' t\u1edbi ASIAD 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u1eabn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. C\u00e1c tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine hay 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Oman \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Ch\u00ednh HLV Park Hang Seo sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Palestine c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u00f4ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa b\u1edfi n\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eaft \u1edf ASIAD 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n thua duy nh\u1ea5t t\u00ednh t\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf trong kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng c\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1eaft x\u00edch y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t trong h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi do c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh th\u1ea5p b\u00e9, l\u1ea1i v\u1eeba tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 hy v\u1ecdng tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD c\u00f9ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n. S\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 NHM c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 an t\u00e2m v\u1ec1 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 th\u1ea7y Park t\u1ea1i ASIAD. Khi m\u00e0 Ti\u1ebfn Linh, \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh hay t\u00e2n binh Ho\u00e0ng Minh Tu\u1ea5n v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i tr\u00f4ng c\u1eady v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t Anh \u0110\u1ee9c n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 ASIAD, s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c \u00e9p s\u1ebd l\u1edbn h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra \u1edf gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng. Hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi n\u00f2ng c\u1ed1t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 v\u1eeba gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin, quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 t\u00edch m\u1edbi \u1edf ASIAD 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Highlight:&nbsp;U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1-0 U23 Oman</strong></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/5/Highlight-U23-Viet-Nam-vs-U23-Oman.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-khen-ngoi-2-cai-ten-xuat-sac-sau-tran-thang-oman-168-193795.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/hlv-park-hang-seo-khen-ngoi-2-cai-ten-xuat-sac-sau-tran-thang-oman.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-khen-ngoi-2-cai-ten-xuat-sac-sau-tran-thang-oman-168-193795.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo khen ng\u1ee3i 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Oman</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khen cho hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u00e0 \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-oman-noi-gi-sau-sieu-pham-ghi-ban-cua-doan-van-hau-168-193794.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/hlv-oman-noi-gi-sau-sieu-pham-ghi-ban-cua-doan-van-hau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-oman-noi-gi-sau-sieu-pham-ghi-ban-cua-doan-van-hau-168-193794.html\">HLV Oman n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu?</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn, HLV Oman cho bi\u1ebft \u00f4ng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi pha ghi b\u00e0n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-le-thuy-hai-chi-ra-han-che-cua-u23-viet-nam-168-193797.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/10/29/hlv-le-thuy-hai-chi-ra-han-che-cua-u23-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-le-thuy-hai-chi-ra-han-che-cua-u23-viet-nam-168-193797.html\">HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 ra h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i kh\u00f3 nh\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc Oman, \u00f4ng L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;&#xA;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5141","checkdouble":"193810"},{"date":"09:59 06/08","title":"Real Madrid s\u1eafp bi\u1ebfn Harry Kane \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/28/real-madrid-sap-bien-harry-kane-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Harry Kane c\u1ee7a Tottenham \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 250 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Spurs nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real \u0111ang g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 trong vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCristiano Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real t\u1edbi Juventus v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 4 n\u0103m, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n CR7. S\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Los Blancos.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Harry Kane v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n c\u1ef1c kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Harry Kane v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n c\u1ef1c kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/Real-Madrid-muon-mua-Harry-Kane-voi-so-tien-cuc-khung-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Hazard v\u00e0 Willian cho Real</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3. Tuy nhi\u00ean, qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng kh\u1ee7ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu \u0111ang g\u1eb7p qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPSG tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Neymar v\u00e0 Mbappe, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Eden Hazard c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm, song Chelsea \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Real d\u00f9 chi t\u1edbi 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/co-hay-khong-viec-real-chi-70-trieu-bang-mua-willian-180-192421.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Wilian c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span>, ngo\u00e0i ra h\u1ecd c\u00f2n nh\u1eafm Christian Pulisic c\u1ee7a Dortmund. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u1ea3 Chelsea v\u00e0 Dortmund \u0111\u1ec1u tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Harry Kane</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Harry Kane c\u1ee7a Tottenham \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 250 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Spurs nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Harry Kane v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n c\u1ef1c kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Harry Kane v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n c\u1ef1c kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/28/real-madrid-sap-bien-harry-kane-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real mu\u1ed1n mua Harry Kane thay th\u1ebf Cristiano Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Harry Kane \u0111\u1ec1u duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c cao, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng trung phong t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Tottenham kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, song Real d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u00f9ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Tottenham b\u00e1n Kane, Real ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 250 tri\u1ec7u euro (t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 222 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng). N\u1ebfu Spurs ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Neymar \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn, Real c\u00f2n cung c\u1ea5p m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 30 tri\u1ec7u euro/m\u00f9a cho Harry Kane, m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00fang b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Ronaldo \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u1edf Juventus. Real \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn trong vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat sinh n\u0103m 1993 \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5140","checkdouble":"193833"},{"date":"10:39 06/08","title":"Lucas Vazquez mu\u1ed1n Real gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0y?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/6/vaz.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Lucas Vazquez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Luka Modric, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha hy v\u1ecdng Real Madrid s\u1ebd gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Modric c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Real \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1eeb khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Real, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Luka Modric \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y. Trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y anh c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Toni Kroos l\u00e0 c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Los Blancos. Modric \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia TBN mang v\u1ec1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lucas Vazquez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Luka Modric h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Lucas Vazquez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Luka Modric h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/19/Lucas-Vazquez-phat-bieu-ve-Luka-Modric-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Modric \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t khi \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. Ronado \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, anh \u0111\u00e3 r\u1eddi Real t\u1edbi Juventus sau 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u00e0 Modric ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u00e1i t\u00ean ti\u1ebfp theo.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia. \u1ede n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, Tottenham, M.U v\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i, \u1edf Italia, Inter Milan c\u0169ng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1985.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 60 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Modric, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia, h\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf c\u1ef1u sao Tottenham.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-nham-muc-tieu-200-trieu-euro-thay-modric-180-193772.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Christian Eriksen</span> c\u1ee7a Tottenham n\u1ebfu Luka Modric ra \u0111i, Los Blancos c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi ra 200 tri\u1ec7u euro mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110an\u00a0M\u1ea1ch. Ngo\u00e0i Eriksen th\u00ec Pjanic c\u1ee7a Juventus hay Ramsey c\u1ee7a Arsenal c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Vazquez mu\u1ed1n Real gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Modric</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lucas Vazquez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Luka Modric, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha hy v\u1ecdng Real Madrid s\u1ebd gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lucas Vazquez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Luka Modric h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Lucas Vazquez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Luka Modric h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/vaz.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Vazquez mu\u1ed1n Real gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Modric</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTrong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. Modric th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, anh \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n anh \u1ea5y ra \u0111i v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u0103m nay\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cRonaldo \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i, Real kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1ea5t th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m n\u1eefa. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Modric, \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1edfi anh \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn. Song t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng Modric \u1edf l\u1ea1i, anh \u1ea5y v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi Real Madrid\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5139","checkdouble":"193838"},{"date":"09:44 06/08","title":"M.U nguy kh\u1ed1n, Mourinho g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea7u c\u1ee9u h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/mu-nguy-khon-mourinho-gui-loi-cau-cuu-hoc-tro.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bayern Munich, HLV Jose Mourinho ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd s\u1edbm h\u1ed9i h\u1ecdp.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nMourinho mong ch\u1edd d\u00e0n sao World Cup<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">G\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tham gia chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, t\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Bayern ho\u1eb7c tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ea1i b\u1ea3n doanh Carrington. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean v\u1eabn bi\u1ec7t t\u00edch, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Paul Pogba &ndash; nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, v\u00e0 Marouane Fellaini &ndash; ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u00e0nh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 c\u00f9ng \u0110T B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Romelu Lukaku v\u00e0 Jesse Lingard \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 quay l\u1ea1i Man United \u0111\u1ec3 luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp. C\u00f2n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Pogba &ndash; Fellaini \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 Hai. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c b\u00f3ng, v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u Premier League &ndash; gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U\" title=\"Jose Mourinho c\u00f4ng khai t\u1ecf th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Ed Woodward \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/mourinho-dang-rat-khong-on-o-man-united.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng n\u00f3i, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng, khi ph\u1ea3i ra qu\u00e2n s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y th\u1ee9 S\u00e1u (r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng th\u1ee9 B\u1ea3y theo gi\u1edd Vi\u1ec7t Nam). \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do Jose Mourinho nh\u01b0 \u0111ang ng\u1ed3i tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ed1ng l\u1eeda. \u00d4ng t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng: &ldquo;Th\u1eadt \u0111en \u0111\u1ee7i khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y th\u1ee9 S\u00e1u.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;N\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i ng\u00e0y Ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 s\u1ebd thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n. Nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd, th\u1ee9 S\u00e1u M.U s\u1ebd ra qu\u00e2n v\u00e0 ng\u00e0y th\u1ee9 Hai, Ba, T\u01b0, N\u0103m l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t. D\u00f9 sao, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ch\u1edd xem s\u1ef1 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a ra s\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Rashford s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay. Lindelof c\u0169ng v\u1eady, Jones v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u1eefa c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u &ndash; 20 ho\u1eb7c 25 ph\u00fat g\u00ec \u0111\u1ea5y. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a l\u1edbn v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 S\u00e1u, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ra qu\u00e2n v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh c\u00f3&rdquo; &ndash; Mourinho ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-ti-nanh-voi-cac-doi-thu-khong-ngung-voi-vinh-bld-man-utd-172-193823.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/mourinho-ti-nanh-voi-cac-doi-thu-khong-ngung-voi-vinh-bld-man-utd.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-ti-nanh-voi-cac-doi-thu-khong-ngung-voi-vinh-bld-man-utd-172-193823.html\">MU thua b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c Bayern, Mourinho ra t\u1ed1i h\u1eadu th\u01b0 cho gi\u1edbi ch\u1ee7</span><br>\r\nT\u1ecb n\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea7m r\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i, HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng n\u1ebfu \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nong-man-utd-chinh-thuc-tim-ra-tan-chu-nhan-cho-ao-so-10-172-193824.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/nong-man-utd-chinh-thuc-tim-ra-chu-nhan-cho-ao-so-10.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nong-man-utd-chinh-thuc-tim-ra-tan-chu-nhan-cho-ao-so-10-172-193824.html\">N\u00f3ng! Man Utd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u00ecm ra t\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n cho \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Marcus Rashford s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n t\u1ea5m \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i \u1edf Old Trafford b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cuc-nong-yerry-mina-toi-ngoai-hang-anh-nhung-khong-phai-mu-172-193827.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/cuc-nong-yerry-mina-toi-ngoai-hang-anh-nhung-khong-phai-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cuc-nong-yerry-mina-toi-ngoai-hang-anh-nhung-khong-phai-mu-172-193827.html\">C\u1ef1c n\u00f3ng: Yerry Mina t\u1edbi Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i MU</span><br>\r\nYerry Mina t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Everton, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Sport c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Goodison Park \u0111ang \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Barca...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5138","checkdouble":"193830"},{"date":"10:40 06/08","title":"T\u00e2n HLV Chelsea chia s\u1ebb kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/31/hlv-sarri-tiet-lo-so-tan-binh-con-lai-cap-ben-chelsea-o-he-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi t\u00e2n HLV. Sau tr\u1eadn, Sarri chia s\u1ebb t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea v\u1edbi m\u1ed1i lo l\u1edbn.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nSarri c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng HLV \u0111\u1eb7t phong c\u00e1ch t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng l\u00e0m t\u00f4n ch\u1ec9, tuy nhi\u00ean Maurizio Sarri kh\u00f4ng t\u00e0i n\u00e0o l\u00e0m kh\u00f3 m\u1ed9t Pep Guardiola gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m h\u01a1n, v\u1edbi h\u01a1n 2 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 c\u00f9ng Man xanh. The Blues \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c 0-2, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Sergio Aguero.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, t\u00e2n HLV Sarri chia s\u1ebb \u00f4ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh: &ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh n\u00e0y s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t bao nhi\u00eau th\u1eddi gian. T\u00f4i m\u1edbi t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 3 tu\u1ea7n, v\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu 6 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t trong tay. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o t\u00f4i, v\u00e0o c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft n\u1eefa.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh r\u1ea5t d\u00e0i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sarri chia s\u1ebb t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea \" title=\"HLV Sarri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/hlv-maurizio-sarri-du-am-tran-chelsea-vs-man-city-sieu-cup-anh-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sarri chia s\u1ebb t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu n\u1eefa v\u1edbi Lyon, v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, thay v\u00ec ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea1y nh\u1ea3y tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1eadp. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia c\u0169ng th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Thibaut Courtois, c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111ang th\u00f4ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u xin Chelsea cho m\u00ecnh ra \u0111i. \u00d4ng cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n nghe tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u1eeb mi\u1ec7ng c\u1ee7a Courtois, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ph\u00eda CLB n\u1eefa. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c cao nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u. Ngo\u00e0i ra, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd ki\u1ebfn g\u00ec v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng tay c\u00f2&rdquo; &ndash; HLV Sarri chia s\u1ebb t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/choi-mo-nhat-barkley-van-duoc-hlv-sarri-bao-ke-172-193816.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/choi-mo-nhat-barkley-van-duoc-hlv-sarri-bao-ke.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/choi-mo-nhat-barkley-van-duoc-hlv-sarri-bao-ke-172-193816.html\">Ch\u01a1i m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t, Barkley v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Sarri b\u1ea3o k\u00ea</span><br>\r\nHLV Sarri \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khen ng\u1ee3i t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Barkley v\u00e0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng anh s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Chelsea trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-02-man-city-co-mot-napoli-phien-ban-loi-xuat-hien-172-193804.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/chelsea-02-man-city-co-mot-napoli-phien-ban-loi-xuat-hien.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-02-man-city-co-mot-napoli-phien-ban-loi-xuat-hien-172-193804.html\">Chelsea 0-2 Man City: C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t Napoli phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n l\u1ed7i xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n</span><br>\r\nHLV Maurizio Sarri t\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 mang theo tri\u1ebft l\u00fd b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 \u1edf Napoli. Tuy nhi\u00ean, tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Man City \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh, h\u1ecd t\u1ecf ra thua k\u00e9m h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n....</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-chelsea-02-man-city-sieu-cup-anh-2018-326-193798.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/video-tong-hop-chelsea-02-man-city-sieu-cup-anh-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-chelsea-02-man-city-sieu-cup-anh-2018-326-193798.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Chelsea 0-2 Man City (Si\u00eau c\u00fap Anh 2018)</span><br>\r\nC\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a Sergio Aguero \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Man City c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea, qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Si\u00eau c\u00fap Anh. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a HLV...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5137","checkdouble":"193831"},{"date":"10:18 06/08","title":"Aaron Ramsey ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn v\u00f2i v\u0129nh Arsenal b\u1eb1ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/6/aaron-ramsey-phu-nhan-voi-vinh-arsenal-bang-luong-khung.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Aaron Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 300.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c The Sun \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i. Song ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ramsey \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00f2i 300.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Aaron Ramsey v\u1edbi Arsenal ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990. Trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Arsenal, b\u1edfi v\u1eady h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 anh ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 chuy\u1ec7n Aaron Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 chuy\u1ec7n Aaron Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/30/Thuc-hu-chuyen-Aaron-Ramsey-roi-Arsenal-neu-khong-co-luong-khung-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ramsey \u0111\u00f2i m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nRamsey x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Arsenal, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u1ebfu nh\u1eefng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn anh s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, n\u1ebfu Arsenal t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i nh\u1eefng mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a Ramsey \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, anh s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb The Sun, Ramsey y\u00eau c\u1ea7u m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 300.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. Vi\u1ec7c Arsenal \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 350.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n cho Mesut Ozil l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales \u0111\u00f2i l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u0169ng theo The Sun, Ramsey \u0111ang g\u00e2y \u00e1p l\u1ef1c bu\u1ed9c Arsenal ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales, trong \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Chelsea, M.U v\u00e0 Man City.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00f4m qua, Mirror kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chi-40-trieu-bang-chelsea-quyet-tam-mua-bang-duoc-sao-khung-arsenal-172-193778.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Ramsey</span>, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chi \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u00c1p l\u1ef1c t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn Arsenal g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng cho Ramsey ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ec3 anh ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ramsey ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn v\u00f2i v\u0129nh Arsenal</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Aaron Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 300.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c The Sun \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i. Song ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 chuy\u1ec7n Aaron Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 chuy\u1ec7n Aaron Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/13/Truoc-tuong-lai-bat-dinh,-Aaron-Ramsey-phat-bieu-ve-Arsenal-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ramsey ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f2i l\u01b0\u01a1ng 300.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n \u1edf b\u1ea3n giao k\u00e8o m\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u01a1 quan \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Ramsey kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c 300.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo ngu\u1ed3n tin \u0111\u1ed9c quy\u1ec1n t\u1eeb Goal, m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 Ramsey y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 200.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb m\u00e0 Arsenal ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nK\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi gia nh\u1eadp Arsenal t\u1eeb Cardiff, Ramsey \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 327 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 ghi 58 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Anh l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Arsenal d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Arsene Wenger, t\u00e2n HLV Emery c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5136","checkdouble":"193837"},{"date":"10:15 06/08","title":"Gi\u00e0nh Si\u00eau c\u00fap Anh, Pep s\u00e1nh ngang\u2026 \u201cNg\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn\u201d David Moyes","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/gianh-sieu-cup-anh-pep-sanh-ngang-nguoi-duoc-chon-david-moyes.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng tin v\u1edb v\u1ea9n, Pep Guardiola s\u00e1nh ngang David Moyes sau chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Community Shield m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nPep c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1edbi Moyes<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh khai h\u1ed9i 1 tu\u1ea7n, tr\u1eadn tranh Community Shield s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra gi\u1eefa nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Premier League v\u00e0 nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 FA Cup. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Man City \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Chelsea v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c 2-0, Kun Aguero l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, Pep Guardiola c\u00f9ng Man City \u0111\u00e3 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch v\u1edbi Man United m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2013-14, th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m &ldquo;Sir&rdquo; David Moyes v\u1eabn c\u00f2n d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, M.U n\u0103m \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ea3 Premier League l\u1eabn Community Shield trong m\u1ed9t n\u0103m, v\u00e0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3t Man City c\u1ee7a Pep v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, M.U v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2012-13 d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sir Alex Ferguson, v\u00e0 danh hi\u1ec7u si\u00eau c\u00fap n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh m\u00e0 h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a David Moyes. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf l\u00e0 k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ec1u g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00fap FA.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gi\u00e0nh si\u00eau c\u00fap Anh, HLV Pep Guardiola s\u00e1nh ngang David Moyes h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gi\u00e0nh si\u00eau c\u00fap Anh, HLV Pep Guardiola s\u00e1nh ngang David Moyes h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/pep.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pep Guardiola s\u00e1nh ngang David Moyes</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u0103m \u0111\u00f3, M.U c\u1ee7a Moyes \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Wigan v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0, Van Persie l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap. 1 n\u0103m sau, \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00fap FA l\u00e0 Arsenal h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0110KV\u0110 Premier League Man City v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-0. Ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3, l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh c\u00fap FA (Arsenal, Man United, Arsenal) \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh Premier League (Chelsea, Leicester, Chelsea). \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi cho r\u1eb1ng, nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch EPL m\u1eafc ph\u1ea3i l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfc si\u00eau c\u00fap Anh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Man xanh \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1 b\u1ecf c\u00e1i d\u1edbp n\u00e0y, khi h\u1ecd h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Chelsea (v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch FA) v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0, tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh CLB \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2013 gi\u00e0nh c\u1ea3 EPL l\u1eabn Community Shield trong m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap Pep Guardiola s\u00e1nh ngang David Moyes.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 v\u1eady, c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n kh\u00e1c, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2010 (Man United) v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League khi gi\u00e0nh si\u00eau c\u00fap Anh ti\u1ec1n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed 2 \u0111\u1ed9i g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Arsenal v\u00e0 Man United, \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 6. \u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i d\u1edbp tr\u00ean con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a Man City.</div>\r\n<div 